CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 14, 1945, pg. 5 reads: "Honeymooning - Mr. and Mrs. Laurence Ross are honeymooning in Detroit, Mich., following their recent marriage. The bride is the former Mrs. Willie Thomas of the North Side, while the groom is a resident of Beltzhoover. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Groom Laurence Ross, and bride Willie Thomas Ross holding bouquet, standing in domestic interior
